 * $Id: dnlcsnoop.d,v 1.1.1.1 2015/09/30 22:01:07 christos Exp $
 *
 * USAGE:	dnlcsnoop.d     # wait several seconds, then hit Ctrl-C
 *
 * FIELDS:
 *		PID             Process ID
 *		CMD          	Command name
 *		TIME         	Elapsed time for lookup, us
 *		HIT          	DNLC hit Y/N
 *		PATH         	Path for DNLC lookup
